<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<
Design 17.2.2017
Proof-of-concept

Constraints:

1) q_pbl > q_inv
2) pblh > cloud base
3) 0 K < t_inv < 15 K
4) cloud base > 30 m
5) pblh < 3000 m 


Variables:

q_inv:          Inversion strength of H2O mixing ratio
tpot_inv:       Inversion strength of liquid potential temperature in K
q_pbl:          H2O mixing ratio, averaged over the planetary boundary layer
tpot_pbl:       Liquid potential temperature in K
pblh:           Planetary boundary layer height
num_pbl:        Number of particles with diameter greater than 50 nm in the PBL 
